special_abilities.description:
A photonic anomaly is a living creature so immense that it functions as a starship (and thus engages only in starship combat). It has no crew, but it can still take engineer, gunner, and pilot actions using the skill bonuses, ranks, and level listed above. Modifiers for its size, speed, and maneuverability have already been factored into its statistics. Critical damage is rolled so that results are applied as follows (
with normal effects per the table
): 1–33, weapons array; 34–66, engines; 67–100, power core.
